title.narrative: Management costs for Programme Coordination Unit (PCU)

description.narrative: This activity (Management costs for Programme Coordination Unit (PCU)) is a component of Impact Programme - Investment to fund innovative solutions for development and help develop sustainable investment markets that work for the poor reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £4,874,135. This component benefits Developing countries, unspecified, and works in the following sector(s): Financial policy and administrative management, Small and medium-sized enterprises (SME) development. , with the following implementing partners: Bank of England , PwC. The start date is 01-12-2012 and the end date is 30-12-2028.
